'''Sant Vincent Pallotti''' ho [[Kristanvponn|Kristi dhormacho]] ek vhodd sant.

== Zolm ani jivit ==
Sant Vincent Pallotti hacho zolm Romachea ek girest pallotti mhuntat tea pallotti de rosia familint 21 abril 1795 zalo.Tache xikxonn San Pious pollotolione scholathaun xikxon korun Romachea collagint tannem xikxonn (prapt) Sopoilem 16 vorsacho astana tanem padri zauchem mhunn tharailem ani maiachea mhoinneachea 16 tarker 1820 tacho (ord zali) padri zalo.

== Vaur ==
Vincent pallolti Romachea kherit phattim urlolea ani durboll nograni lokam pasot vavurlo. Mariache ani povitr tritveche ojap hacher tacho chodd bhavart aslo tea kallar pap saybak sant manun ghetlo. Kherit bhaxen taka vegllea-vegllea desachea bhagani devache utor (dhorm prochar) porgottunk mhunn dhadlo ani apostalanchi dhorm sobha sodun kadli. San Paulachea atmear tannem chodd bhurvaso kelo. Te mallear devak aslole sogllea munxa kullachi soddvonn ani tem tannem mogan dovorun catholic dhorm sobha suru korpachem tachem sopon zaun aslem
sogllea firgojeni (ekchar) ekvottaichi ani padriponnachea jivitak svikarkorunk lokank tannem fuddavo kelo punn hea tache jivitant ghoddle tem tannem aplea lagim zata titli urba vadovpache mhunn chintlem. Pallotti Vatican vishwa-sonstecho askari zalo kitek tache firgojent lokam modem ekchar vadoupache vatican 2che vixoi zaun aslo .

== Altaracho Man ==
Sant Vincent Pallottiche moron janierchea 22-1850 Romache papal xaran (rajean) zalem sonvxoda kani tachi kudd 1900-1950 sodun kaddli tednan tachi kudd soglich kusloli. Povtir Sobhechea nema pormanem tachi kudd Sant Salvatoes Onde Romachea firgojent dovrleli astana povitrtayen polleounk mellta te baxhen porzollit zali tori astana 1963 hea Rorsa Papsaib XXIII hannem Sant Vincent Pallottik bhagevont mhunn porgottlo.









